Developer Terms of Use
des:
This app is for a busy person with lots to do and remember. Whats lacking from most reminder apps is the ability to rank the most important task. This app solves that problem.

Phrases: 
Add {task} - to add a task 
Delete {Task} - To delete a task
Move {task}. - to change a rank of data 
Delete all data in the database - to remove all data
Show all 
Remind me of something - > Remind of {Task} daily or once.
